						"content": "var w = rect.getWidth(),\n    h = rect.getHeight(),\n    m = w / 5;\ncanvas.fillEllipse(rect.x1 + m, rect.y1, rect.x2, rect.y2);\ncanvas.ellipse(rect.x1 + m, rect.y1, rect.x2, rect.y2);\ncanvas.line(rect.x1, rect.y1, rect.x1, rect.y2);\ncanvas.line(rect.x1, rect.y1 + h/2, rect.x1 + m, rect.y1 + h/2);\n"
